rauma: Case Reports and Overview</a></div><div class="related__authors"><ul class="rlist--inline loa mobile-authors loa-height"><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Campbell D. Tait</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">B. K. Somani</span></li></ul></div><div class="meta">2012Jan1 | Case Reports in Urology, Vol. 2012</div></div><div class="getFTR external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1155/2012/207872">Crossref</a></div></div></li><li class="citedByEntry" data-doi="10.1017/CBO9780511793950.008"><div class="related"><div class="related__title"><a target="_blank" href="https://doi.org/10.1017/CBO9780511793950.008">Genitourinary and breast radiology</a></div><div class="related__authors"><ul class="rlist--inline loa mobile-authors loa-height"></ul></div><div class="meta">2011Nov3</div></div><div class="getFTR external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1017/CBO9780511793950.008">Crossref</a></div></div></li><li class="citedByEntry" data-doi="10.1007/174_2011_470"><div class="related"><div class="related__title"><a target="_blank" href="https://doi.org/10.1007/174_2011_470">Kidney, Ureter, Adrenal Gland</a></div><div class="related__authors"><ul class="rlist--inline loa mobile-authors loa-height"><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Michael K. Scherr</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Ulrich Linsenmaier</span></li></ul></div><div class="meta">2011Jan1</div></div><div class="getFTR external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1007/174_2011_470">Crossref</a></div></div></li><li class="citedByEntry" data-doi="10.1007/978-3-642-16892-5_7"><div class="related"><div class="related__title"><a target="_blank" href="https://doi.org/10.1007/978-3-642-16892-5_7">Genitourinary</a></div><div class="related__authors"><ul class="rlist--inline loa mobile-authors loa-height"><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">María I. Martínez